{"tid":2349452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"企鵝妹爆不畏疫情「飛瑞典找乾爹過夜」！　網抓包：有吃避孕藥","createTime":"2021-01-01T14:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T15:10:16.000Z","uid":117934,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab87e02600084a2a9f3db2c523f9faacb989fd29","tid":2349452,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣實況主「企鵝妹」柳允進（윰찌니，Jinny）過去因為清純的形象在台灣爆紅，近年轉往歐美發展，也大改過往風格，前陣子才在直播大聊自己的性愛史，近日又遭國外網友爆料疑似跟乾爹過夜，還吃了避孕藥，文章被翻譯後搬到台灣論壇，也引起了一陣熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20201210111115-681a98d49aa6069a0ab8c758c1d0f6a4-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20201210111115-681a98d49aa6069a0ab8c758c1d0f6a4-mobile.jpg&h=e1fe8ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有眼尖的國外網友在「Reddit」上傳了一份標題為「Jinny &amp; Najn」的文件，被熱心台灣網友翻譯後轉貼到「遊戲大亂鬥」論壇，文中透露企鵝妹在9月跟朋友一起去歐洲旅行數月，但疫情惡化後，朋友迅速返韓，她卻堅持待在當地，才引發了該名網友的好奇心，仔細觀察後竟從許多蛛絲馬跡中發現「企鵝妹與乾爹過夜」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20201210111125-30562858ef31c949e4257e3263928bb6-mobile.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20201210111125-30562858ef31c949e4257e3263928bb6-mobile.png&h=c011f97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據該網友調查結果，企鵝妹在9月在瑞典跟大乾爹初次見面，隔天兩人就去約會，一個月之後還放了一天假在德國陪對方，隨後跟著男方返回瑞典共度兩周時間。在這期間，她在回到南韓後，曾聲稱要去找老朋友，但隨後在開台時卻被抓包口罩款式跟瑞典乾爹一樣，疑似又偷偷飛回瑞典約會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5365/d5365233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5365%2Fd5365233.jpg&h=3eba6cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，爆料文中也提到，企鵝妹曾表示自己「不排斥無套」，而在疑似與乾爹相處的期間，開台詢問網友關於避孕藥的相關資訊，幾個禮拜的時間後，又自曝在瑞典時變得很愛哭，情緒起伏很大，並直言「可能是吃了避孕藥後的副作用」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQjsSycU4AIB9ks.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEQjsSycU4AIB9ks.jpg%3Alarge&h=fead2c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友紛紛讚嘆該爆料文的調查內容精細，留言「福爾摩斯轉世嗎？」、「爆料一出，會有一堆火山孝子瘋狂抖內搶當下一個了」、「只是為了做x就飛出國也太克難了吧」、「超猛的調查」等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/63/5b/b6/635bb6dcffcf64d778c45627c4b70f63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F63%2F5b%2Fb6%2F635bb6dcffcf64d778c45627c4b70f63.jpg&h=b5c59671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dff138f9e43c399b9bb78b4b7da7363b371a15a","tid":2349452,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"湊下鬼啫<br />\n<br />\n點解話係契爺"},{"pid":"e368297bbffcfc6a48c0b9af623730c2255378c8","tid":2349452,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6f84258d4dcc8fe92fb9c2adc176201856f8cc","tid":2349452,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"c2dca8739c8024582f44cdefb5c796845dd68ec5","tid":2349452,"uid":290393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9dff138f9e43c399b9bb78b4b7da7363b371a15a","tid":2349452,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"湊下鬼啫<br />\n<br />\n點解話係契爺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:00:43.000Z","msg":"我都唔明, 溝下鬼仔唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca978d0467b0b2737ce16e6b97a05261ab028d1","tid":2349452,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2dca8739c8024582f44cdefb5c796845dd68ec5","tid":2349452,"uid":290393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9dff138f9e43c399b9bb78b4b7da7363b371a15a","tid":2349452,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"湊下鬼啫<br />\n<br />\n點解話係契爺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:00:43.000Z","msg":"我都唔明, 溝下鬼仔唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"仲以為係大肚腩禿頭"},{"pid":"85311bf3c6a3399d4011e32ce0eba636ef2d0f4c","tid":2349452,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:06:12.000Z","msg":"原來咁淫"},{"pid":"bea917d44db90752c7d1dc62d94796f93a25b94a","tid":2349452,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"外國腸頂到上肺腑<br />\n係爽啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c933c490e754053641fa9c45c12fe4384223c3c","tid":2349452,"uid":361975,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"85311bf3c6a3399d4011e32ce0eba636ef2d0f4c","tid":2349452,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:06:12.000Z","msg":"原來咁淫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"我對住條鬼仔仲撚淫連避孕藥都唔食<br />\n<br />\n利申：有棍"}]}